  ('PG Certification in Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing-pg', 'From MICA Ahmedabad', 'Comprehensive digital marketing program covering SEO, performance marketing, and growth strategies.', 5, 'MICA Ahmedabad', 'Prof. Shailendra Pratap Jain', 'Professor, MICA', 24, 95000, 135000, 1, 2699, 'Intermediate', 4.5, 5670, 22000, 14, 280, 'PG Certificate', 'SEO,SEM,Google Ads,Facebook Marketing,Content Marketing,Analytics,Email Marketing,Growth Hacking', 'Live campaigns with real budgets,MICA campus visit,Industry mentor from Google/Meta,Portfolio of 10+ campaigns', 0, 1, '2026-03-25'),
