  ('Advanced Certificate in Data Science & Analytics', 'data-science-analytics', 'From IIT Delhi', 'Learn statistical analysis, predictive modeling, and business intelligence from IIT Delhi professors.', 1, 'IIT Delhi', 'Prof. Amitabha Bagchi', 'Professor, IIT Delhi', 30, 165000, 225000, 1, 4599, 'Intermediate', 4.7, 2340, 9800, 14, 300, 'Advanced Certificate', 'Python,R,SQL,Tableau,Power BI,Statistics,Predictive Modeling,EDA', 'IIT Delhi campus immersion,Real company datasets,Industry mentor matching,Career transition support', 0, 1, '2026-04-05'),
